    "Only two works [24,25] in the literature have dedicated attention to dysgraphia diagnosis.",
    "However, the first work offers only a cursory overview of machine learning-based methods for diagnosing dysgraphia, lacking in-depth explanation regarding the details of feature engineering in machine learning model development.",
